      <section eId="sec_15_21_1">
        <num>15-21-1</num>
        <content>
          <p>Every fine imposed by a court under the authority of this Code shall be paid immediately or within such reasonable time as the court may grant.</p>
          <p>(Laws 1833, Cobb's 1851 Digest, p. 837; Code 1863, § 4541; Code 1868, § 4561; Code 1873, § 4655; Code 1882, § 4655; Penal Code 1895, § 1084; Penal Code 1910, § 1111; Code 1933, § 27-2901.)</p>
